('enterprise-design-review-gate', 'data-center-and-reliability-design', 'checkpoint', 'assessment', NULL, NULL, 'Enterprise Design Review Gate', 'Review checkpoint for Data Center and Reliability Design. The learner consolidates evidence from Spine-Leaf Data Center Concepts, Overlay and Underlay Concepts, Disaster Recovery and Backup Connectivity, SLA SLO and Availability Thinking, identifies unresolved prerequisite gaps, and decides whether to continue, review selected topics, or complete extra practice before the next roadmap segment.', 8, 'checkpoint', 3, 'advanced', '{"reviewFocus":"Review checkpoint for Data Center and Reliability Design. The learner consolidates evidence from Spine-Leaf Data Center Concepts, Overlay and Underlay Concepts, Disaster Recovery and Backup Connectivity, SLA SLO and Availability Thinking, identifies unresolved prerequisite gaps, and decides whether to continue, review selected topics, or complete extra practice before the next roadmap segment.","reviewCriteria":["List the roadmap items reviewed for this checkpoint.","Provide one evidence artifact such as notes, a diagram, a lab result, code, queries, screenshots, or a project review.","Record at least two gaps, risks, or follow-up actions, or explicitly state that no critical gaps were found.","Use the result to choose one next step: continue, review selected topics, or complete extra practice."],"source":"roadmap.sh/network-engineer"}'::jsonb, true, true, '["Summarize the main concepts and decisions from Data Center and Reliability Design in practical network engineering terms.", "Identify prerequisite gaps, unclear topics, or risks that should be reviewed before moving forward.", "Create a short evidence artifact that links completed roadmap items to what was learned."]'::jsonb, '["List the roadmap items reviewed for this checkpoint.", "Provide one evidence artifact such as notes, a diagram, a lab result, code, queries, screenshots, or a project review.", "Record at least two gaps,